---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Aegean Dispatch" description="What Aegean Dispatch is and who's behind it.">
  <section class="page--narrow" style="margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 class="heading" style="font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);">About Aegean Dispatch</h1>
    <p class="subheading" style="margin: 0 0 1rem;">
      A personal blog based on the Aegean coast. Expect regular notes on cinema, technology, books, and sport.
    </p>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      <h3 class="heading" style="margin: 0 0 0.4rem;">The idea</h3>
      <p class="text-muted" style="margin: 0;">
        Aegean Dispatch is meant to be light, legible, and focused on the writing. Each post is written in Markdown,
        published statically with Astro, and organized for easy browsing by topic.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="heading" style="margin: 0 0 0.4rem;">About the author</h3>
      <p class="text-muted" style="margin: 0 0 0.8rem;">
        I split time between developing software tools, watching and thinking about movies, and training for a marathon I'll definitely run in 3 years. This site is a quiet notebook
        for the things worth keeping: a good line from a book, a scene from a movie that stuck with me, a piece of software that stays out of the way.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted" style="margin: 0;">
        If you have feedback or want to collaborate, drop a note via your preferred channel. I'm always up for new ideas.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
      <h3 class="heading" style="margin: 0 0 0.4rem;">Find me elsewhere</h3>
      <p class="text-muted" style="margin: 0 0 0.6rem;">Links to my socials.</p>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a class="card-link" href="https://github.com/ErdagEge" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub · @ErdagEge</a>
        <a class="card-link" href="https://x.com/EgeErdag" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Twitter · @EgeErdag</a>
        <a class="card-link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/egeerdag/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn · egeerdag</a>
        <a class="card-link" href="https://open.spotify.com/show/5IkatgeB5ZBbbAADZC9Tty?si=1737e6df98b144b8" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
          Spotify · Açık Büfe Diyalog
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
